Files in this folder use MySQL C API (libmysqlclient) version 9.6.0.

  Version : MySQL 9.6.0

macOS
-----
  Source  : Homebrew mysql-client formula
  Formula : mysql-client
  Prefix  : /opt/homebrew/opt/mysql-client

  To rebuild prebuilt/lib/mac/libmysql.a:
    brew install mysql-client
    sh prebuilt/scripts/build-libmysql-mac-arm64.sh

Windows
-------
  Source  : Scoop mysql package (mysql-9.6.0-winx64)
  Install : scoop install mysql

  After installing, run setup-mysql-win.bat (in the repo root) once to copy
  libmysql.lib and libmysql.dll from the Scoop installation into the project's
  prebuilt directories.  build-engine-x64.bat calls this automatically if
  libmysql.lib is missing.

  Files populated by setup-mysql-win.bat:
    prebuilt/unpacked/Thirdparty/x86_64-win32-v142_static_Debug/lib/libmysql.lib
    build-win-x86_64/livecode/Debug/lib/libmysql.lib
    build-win-x86_64/livecode/Debug/libmysql.dll   (runtime dependency)
